imdb.plot outline: Hello! Hollywood airs on 35 TV stations in China, unspools on Tencent and is on all the high-speed trains.It is also broadcast in New York, San Francisco and Los Angeles. The show is hosted by Yi Tian in Los Angeles and Andy Dong in Beijing.
imdb.title: Hello! Hollywood
plot: Join our host, Andy Dong, and field reporter, Yangyang Cheng, as they take you inside the elite Hollywood celebrity lifestyles! Get industry details and information, landmark tours and more, packed into one entertainment news program.::Anonymous
